data.description: AMAZING stone country cottage in the middle of Oakmont with a BEAUTIFUL mature wooded/PRIVATE .53 acre lot. This true 4 floor multi-level with just a few steps between the 4 FANTASTIC floors offers easy accessibility to the 3 exterior accesses. From the great sized eat in kitchen (banquette included)to the sun drenched L-shaped dining/living room with the most AMAZING picture windows,curved wall&gas fireplace to the 3 awesome sized bedrooms(master w/full bath) you will LOVE this FABULOUS home. The first lower level features lots of newer planked vinyl flooring,a flex space/office area,family room with great natural light & freshly painted walls,powder room,HUGE storage and laundry room with exterior access. The 4th&lowest of the floors is an AMAZING sized game room w/bar, gas fireplace,another FABULOUS picture window & exterior access to the STUNNING rear yard. Lots of harwood floors,newer furnace,AC&roof. Sewer line was lined 2 years ago. SUPER convenient to everything Oakmont offers.
